													<div id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1613459794853" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module widget-type-rich_text" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module"><span id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1613459794853_" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_rich_text" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="rich_text"><h4 style="margin-bottom: 0.625rem;">Privacy Policy</h4><p><i>(LAST MODIFIED ON MARCH. 17 2021)</i></p><p>Welcome to the Ethical Research Solutions Website! This Privacy Policy (the “Policy”) explains the privacy practices of Ethical Research Solutions. (<strong style="color: #272930;">“Ethical Research Solutions”</strong>, “<strong style="color: #272930;">we</strong>”, <strong style="color: #272930;">“us”</strong> or <strong style="color: #272930;">“our”</strong>) which apply to Ethical Research Solutions’s website located at <a href="indexc6eb.html?hsLang=en">http://ethicalresearchsolution.com</a>, which is owned and operated by Ethical Research Solutions, and includes all subdomains, present and future (the <strong style="color: #272930;">“Website”</strong>), including your participation in surveys and the provision of Testimonials (as defined below).</p><p>Additional definitions may be made throughout this Policy, but they will be recognizable as they will be capitalized, bolded, and in quotation marks. Additional definitions may also be found in the <a href="terms-of-use.html?hsLang=en">Terms of Use</a> (the “TOU”), and will have the same meaning in this Policy as they do there. The definitions found in this Policy shall also apply to the TOU.</p><p><i><strong style="color: #272930;">By visiting or using the Website, you agree to be bound by the terms of this Policy. If you do not agree to all the provisions contained in the Policy, you are not authorized to use the Website.</strong></i></p><p>Ethical Research Solutions reserves the right, at any time and without prior notice, to modify or replace any of the Policy. Any changes to the Policy can be found at this URL. It is your responsibility to check the Policy periodically for changes. Your use of the Website following the posting of any changes to the Policy constitutes acceptance of those changes. If there are any significant changes to the Policy that materially affect the way we treat your information, you will be notified by email.</p><p>The Policy should be read in conjunction with the <a href="terms-of-use.html?hsLang=en">TOU</a>, as both these documents govern your use of the Website.</p><p>If you have any questions about the Policy or if you wish to inquire about and / or access any Personal Information (as defined below) Ethical Research Solutions holds about you, please contact: Ethical Research Solutions France at <a href="mailto:info@ethicalresearchsolution.com">info@ethicalresearchsolution.com</a> or at 71 rue Réaumur, 75002 Paris France.</p></span>
													</div>
