										<div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-row">
											<div class="row-fluid ">
												<div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" style="" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" data-w="12">
													<div id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1613460054417" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module">
														<div class="custom-one-col-content-wrap">
															<h5>1. General Statement of Privacy</h5>
															<div class="custom-one-col-content-col">
																<p>Ethical Research Solutions takes your privacy and security of Personal Information (as defined below) very seriously. We have provided a secure environment and this strict Policy that describes the limited ways the information is used and the limited access to such information</p>
															</div>
														</div>
													</div>
												</div>
											</div>
										</div>
										<div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row">
											<div class="row-fluid ">
												<div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" style="" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" data-w="12">
													<div id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1613460124870" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module">
														<div class="custom-one-col-content-wrap">
															<h5>2. Scope of Policy</h5>
															<div class="custom-one-col-content-col">
																<p><strong>Personal Information.</strong> This Policy covers the processing of information relating to an identified or identifiable natural person (<strong>“Personal Information”</strong>) gathered by Ethical Research Solutions when you are using the Website and provide insights and opinions when answering our surveys. This Policy also covers Ethical Research Solutions’s processing of any Personal Information that Ethical Research Solutions may share with its business partners or other third parties under very limited circumstances.</p>
																<p><strong>Third Party Services.</strong> This Policy does not apply to the general practices and processing of information (whether personal or not) by third parties that Ethical Research Solutions does not own or control, including but not limited to any third-party websites or services (<strong>“Third-Party Website”</strong> or <strong>“Third-Party Service”</strong>) that you elect to access through the Website or via a link from the Website. While we attempt to facilitate access or link only to those Third-Party Websites or Services that share our respect for your privacy, we cannot take responsibility for the content or privacy policies of those Third-Party Websites or Third-Party Services. We encourage you to carefully review the privacy policies of any Third-Party Website you access or Third-Party Service you use.</p>
																<p><strong>Limited Collection.</strong> Ethical Research Solutions does not gather any of your Personal Information while you are using the Website, except as provided in this Policy. Where you have provided Personal Information or where we have collected Personal Information, it will only be used for the stated purpose, as detailed more specifically in the next sections.</p>
																<p><strong>Personal Information collected, purposes and legal basis.</strong> The following is a list of Personal Information that Ethical Research Solutions may collect from you when you use the Website and what we use it for.</p>
																<ul>
																	<li>While visiting the Website, participating in surveys or providing a Testimonial you may be required to provide the following accurate and truthful Personal Information: first name, email address, age, gender, postal code, marital status, primary occupation and household income. You may also choose to provide us with additional Personal Information when you fill out free fields in our questionnaires. These Personal Information are used by Ethical Research Solutions, in the context of the consumer surveys it conducts on behalf of its customers, leading to the establishment and transmission of statistics. Ethical Research Solutions's activities actually consist in conducting surveys on behalf of its client towards a targeted audience. Ethical Research Solutions determines the questions asked, and therefore, some of the Personal Information required, depending on the purpose and nature of the survey in question, as well as on the expected results. The processing of such Personal Information is based on your express consent.</li>
																	<li>When you visit the Website to access the results of a survey, as a customer of Ethical Research Solutions, you provide Personal Information, such as your e-mail address, first and last name. This processing is carried out on the basis of the execution of the contract between you and Ethical Research Solutions.</li>
																	<li>We may also use your Personal Information to contact you with newsletters, marketing or promotional materials and other information that may be of interest to you as further described in Section 5 (Mailing List Management). In particular, Ethical Research Solutions may contact you individually following a survey or a Testimonial to provide you with information that may be of interest to you. Such processing is based on your express consent. If you have not consented to the reception of such communications, Ethical Research Solutions will not contact you for this purpose.</li>
																	<li>When visiting the Website, Ethical Research Solutions may collect information through cookies, as further described in Section 9 of this Policy and in the Cookie Policy accessible <a href="cookie-policy.html?hsLang=en">here </a>.</li>
																</ul>
															</div>
														</div>
													</div>
												</div>
											</div>
										</div>
										<div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row">
											<div class="row-fluid ">
												<div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" style="" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" data-w="12">
													<div id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1613460154907" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module">
														<div class="custom-one-col-content-wrap">
															<h5>3. Non-disclosure of Personal Information to Third Parties</h5>
															<div class="custom-one-col-content-col">
																<p><strong>Limited Disclosure.</strong> Except as provided in this Section 3, and in Sections 5 (Mailing List Management) and 6 (Security and Encryption of Information) and unless Ethical Research Solutions’s users expressly consent to receive commercial electronic messages from identified third parties, in which case Ethical Research Solutions would only communicate to such third parties the email addresses of consenting users, Ethical Research Solutions does not divulge any Personal Information collected via the Website to third parties.</p>
																<p>Moreover, subject to situations where Ethical Research Solutions’s users expressly consent to receive commercial electronic messages from identified third parties, in which case Ethical Research Solutions may sell, rent, trade or license to such third parties the email addresses of consenting users, Ethical Research Solutions does not sell, rent, trade or license any Personal Information regarding its users to third parties. Only the employees, representatives, subcontractors, officers, agents, or assigns of Ethical Research Solutions (collectively, the <strong>“Representatives” </strong>) are responsible for the management and development of the Website, and only these individuals have access to the information collected there. These Representatives all have been instructed to comply with the Policy.</p>
																<p>We may share any information we have collected about you or that you have submitted (whether Personal Information or not):</p>
																<ul>
																	<li>in response to subpoenas, court orders, or legal process, or to establish, protect, or exercise our legal rights or defend against legal claims or demands;</li>
																	<li>if we believe it is necessary in order to investigate, prevent, or take action regarding illegal activities, fraud, or situations involving potential threats to the safety of any person, or any violation of the TOU;</li>
																	<li>if we believe it is necessary to investigate, prevent, or take action regarding situations that involve abuse of the Website infrastructure or the Internet in general (such as voluminous spamming, denial of service attacks, or attempts to compromise the security of the Website infrastructure or the Website generally);</li>
																	<li>to a parent company, subsidiaries, joint ventures, or other companies under common control with Ethical Research Solutions (in which case we will require such entities to honour this Policy) to properly create consumer research reports or to carry out geolocated campaigns ;</li>
																	<li>if Ethical Research Solutions merges with another entity, is subject to a corporate reorganization, sells or transfers all or part of its business, assets or shares (in which case we will require such entity to assume our obligations under this Policy, or inform you that you are covered by a new privacy policy).</li>
																</ul>
															</div>
														</div>
													</div>
												</div>
											</div>
										</div>
										<div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-6 dnd-row">
											<div class="row-fluid ">
												<div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" style="" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" data-w="12">
													<div id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1613460196755" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module">
														<div class="custom-one-col-content-wrap">
															<h5>4. Collection, Use, and Disclosure of Non-personal Information</h5>
															<div class="custom-one-col-content-col">
																<p><strong>Usage Information.</strong> We collect information about usage of the Website from within the Website (<strong>“Usage Information”</strong>), but none of this information identifies you personally. For example, each time you use the Website, we automatically collect the list of most used screens by users. Usage Information can also consist in your testimonials and answers (<strong>“Testimonials”</strong>) to the questions we ask you within the framework of surveys available on the Website with the purpose of obtaining your views on local retail projects and various consuming habits you may have (<strong>“Surveys”</strong>). We use Usage Information collected in this manner (i) to better understand your needs and the needs of the Website users in the aggregate; (ii) for statistical purposes to keep track of the usage of the Website with a view to introducing improvements; (iii) for statistical purposes to synthetize your (and other Website users’) views and opinions collected through the Surveys; and (iv) to trace any fraudulent or criminal activity, or any activity in violation of the TOU. In this context, Ethical Research Solutions may also contact you individually to provide you with information that may be of interest to you if you gave your consent to such communications.</p>
																<p><strong>Limited Disclosure.</strong> We may share certain Usage Information with third parties so as to optimize our Website, provide statistics on the use of our Website and provide statistics on your views and opinions collected through the Surveys, or provide targeted marketing offers.</p>
															</div>
														</div>
													</div>
												</div>
											</div>
										</div>
										<div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-7 dnd-row">
											<div class="row-fluid ">
												<div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" style="" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" data-w="12">
													<div id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1613460234435" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module">
														<div class="custom-one-col-content-wrap">
															<h5>5. Mailing List Management</h5>
															<div class="custom-one-col-content-col">
																<p><strong>Third Party Service Providers.</strong> Ethical Research Solutions may use Third-Party Services to manage our mailing list and send out emails. In which case, Personal Information is transferred to such Third-Party Service providers in order for the mailing list to function properly. Your Personal Information is only used for the proper sending out of email. If Ethical Research Solutions uses any such Third-Party Service provider, it will obtain representations from them that they do not use this Personal Information for any other purpose and will not transfer or sell your Personal Information to any other third party.</p>
																<p><strong>Unsubscribe.</strong> You may unsubscribe from Ethical Research Solutions’s mailing list at any time, by following the link at the bottom of all Ethical Research Solutions emails, by using the following link: <a href="https://app.ethicalresearchsolution.com/en/community/subscriptions/edit" rel="noopener" target="_blank">https://app.ethicalresearchsolution.com/en/community/subscriptions/edit</a> or by contacting us at <a href="mailto:info@ethicalresearchsolution.com">info@ethicalresearchsolutionc.com</a>.</p>
															</div>
														</div>
													</div>
												</div>
											</div>
										</div>
										<div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-8 dnd-row">
											<div class="row-fluid ">
												<div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" style="" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" data-w="12">
													<div id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1613460274767" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module">
														<div class="custom-one-col-content-wrap">
															<h5>6. Security and Encryption of Information</h5>
															<div class="custom-one-col-content-col">
																<p><strong>Security.</strong> Ethical Research Solutions uses only industry best practices (physical, electronic and procedural) in keeping any data collected (including Personal Information) secure. In addition, Ethical Research Solutions uses third-party vendors and hosting partners to provide the necessary hardware, software, networking, storage, and related technology required to run the Website, and these third parties have been selected for their reliability in terms of security, both electronic and physical. You acknowledge that our third-party vendors and hosting partners may be located in jurisdictions or countries where the privacy laws may not be as protective as those in your home province, state, country or other governmental jurisdiction.</p>
																<p><strong>Risks Associated with the Internet or Wireless Data Transmission.</strong> Despite Ethical Research Solutions’s best efforts to ensure third parties will not access or obtain your Personal Information through the Website, complete confidentiality and security cannot currently be guaranteed on the Internet and/or where data is transferred via wireless digital technology of any type. Communication in this manner is subject to interception, loss, or alteration. You acknowledge and agree that Ethical Research Solutions cannot be held responsible for any losses or damages whether pecuniary or otherwise resulting from the transmission of your Personal Information in this manner and that such communications are at your own risk.</p>
															</div>
														</div>
													</div>
												</div>
											</div>
										</div>
										<div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-9 dnd-row">
											<div class="row-fluid ">
												<div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module" style="" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" data-w="12">
