																	<br>You can request to access to your Personal Information directly via the following link: <a href="https://app.ethicalresearchsolution.com/en/community/data-requests/new" rel="noopener" target="_blank">https://app.ethicalresearchsolution.com/en/community/data-requests/new</a> 
																	<br>You can also request the restriction of the processing or object to the processing of your Personal Information under the conditions provided by the applicable regulations. Finally, when the processing of your Personal Information is based on your consent, you have the right to withdraw your consent at any time.
																	<br>
																	<br>You can exercise your rights by contacting: <a href="mailto:support@ethicalresearchsolution.com">support@ethicalresearchsolution.com</a> or send your request to 71 rue Réaumur, 75002 Paris France.
																	<br>
																	<br>You also have the right to file a complaint with the Commission Nationale de l'Informatique et des Libertés ("CNIL") if you consider that the processing of your Personal Information by Ethical Research Solutions does not comply with the applicable regulations.</p>
																<p>You have the right not to receive discriminatory treatment for the exercise of the privacy rights conferred by the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA).</p>
