																<p><strong>Privacy.</strong> This Policy and Ethical Research Solutions’s practices in general are designed to be in compliance with the EU Regulation 2016/679 of the European Parliament and of the Council of 27 April 2016 on the processing of personal data and on the free movement of such data (<strong>"GDPR"</strong>) and the French Act n°78-17 of 6 January 1978 on information technology, data files and civil liberties (<strong>"LIL"</strong>). If you have any questions regarding this compliance, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@ethicalresearchsolution.com">info@ethicalresearchsolution.com</a>.
