																<p><strong>Anti-Spam.</strong> Ethical Research Solutions is committed to ensuring that we respect anti-spam legislation, specifically the Directive 2002/58/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 12 July 2002 concerning the processing of personal data and the protection of privacy in the electronic communications sector (Directive on privacy and electronic communications). If you feel you have received emails from us in violation of these laws, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@ethicalresearchsolution.com">support@ethicalresearchsolution.com</a>.
